toArray \- Return the result set as an array.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]\f[I]query.toArray()\f[]\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
SdbQuery
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Return the result set as an array.
.SH PARAMETERS
.PP
NULL
.SH RETURN VALUE
.PP
On success, return result set as an array.
.PP
On error, exception will be thrown.
.SH ERRORS
.PP
when exception happen, use getLastError() to get the error code and use
getLastErrMsg() to get error message.
For more detial, please reference to Troubleshooting.
